{
  "script_id": "parametric",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "欢迎来到参数方程实验！今天我们要学习描述曲线的另一种方式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "你已经熟悉了 y 等于 f(x) 这种函数形式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "但有些曲线，比如圆，用这种形式很难表示。参数方程就是解决方案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "参数方程用一个参数 t 来同时表示 x 和 y。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 41040,
      "text": "形式是 x 等于 f(t)，y 等于 g(t)，其中 t 在某个范围内变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "当 t 变化时，点 (x, y) 就在平面上画出一条曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "参数 t 可以理解为时间，曲线就是点随时间运动的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "circle-1",
      "filename": "circle-circle-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/circle-circle-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.25,
      "size": 20016,
      "text": "最经典的例子是圆的参数方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "circle-2",
      "filename": "circle-circle-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/circle-circle-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "圆心在原点、半径为 r 的圆：x 等于 r cos t，y 等于 r sin t。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "circle-3",
      "filename": "circle-circle-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/circle-circle-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "参数 t 就是角度，从 0 到 2π 变化一周。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "circle-4",
      "filename": "circle-circle-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/circle-circle-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "这比用 x 平方加 y 平方等于 r 平方来描述圆要方便得多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-1",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/ellipse-ellipse-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.24,
      "size": 19872,
      "text": "椭圆的参数方程是圆的推广。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-2",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/ellipse-ellipse-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "x 等于 a cos t，y 等于 b sin t，其中 a 和 b 是长短半轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-3",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/ellipse-ellipse-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.37,
      "size": 21888,
      "text": "当 a 等于 b 时，椭圆就退化为圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "ellipse",
      "line_id": "ellipse-4",
      "filename": "ellipse-ellipse-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/ellipse-ellipse-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "参数 t 不再是几何角度，但仍然从 0 到 2π 画完整个椭圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cycloid-1",
      "filename": "cycloid-cycloid-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/cycloid-cycloid-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "摆线是一个有趣的曲线，它是圆在直线上滚动时圆周上一点的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cycloid-2",
      "filename": "cycloid-cycloid-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/cycloid-cycloid-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.67,
      "size": 42768,
      "text": "参数方程是 x 等于 r 乘以 t 减 sin t，y 等于 r 乘以 1 减 cos t。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cycloid-3",
      "filename": "cycloid-cycloid-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/cycloid-cycloid-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.48,
      "size": 23616,
      "text": "摆线有一个神奇的性质：它是最速降线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "cycloid",
      "line_id": "cycloid-4",
      "filename": "cycloid-cycloid-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/cycloid-cycloid-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "也就是说，小球沿摆线滑下比沿直线滑下更快到达终点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lissajous-1",
      "filename": "lissajous-lissajous-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/lissajous-lissajous-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "利萨如图形是两个简谐振动合成的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lissajous-2",
      "filename": "lissajous-lissajous-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/lissajous-lissajous-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "参数方程是 x 等于 A sin(at 加 δ)，y 等于 B sin(bt)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lissajous-3",
      "filename": "lissajous-lissajous-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/lissajous-lissajous-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "调整频率比 a 比 b 和相位差 δ，可以得到各种美丽的图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "lissajous",
      "line_id": "lissajous-4",
      "filename": "lissajous-lissajous-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/lissajous-lissajous-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "当 a 比 b 是简单整数比时，图形是闭合的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "advantages",
      "line_id": "advantages-1",
      "filename": "advantages-advantages-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/advantages-advantages-1.mp3",
      "duration": 0.98,
      "size": 15696,
      "text": "参数方程有很多优势。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "advantages",
      "line_id": "advantages-2",
      "filename": "advantages-advantages-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/advantages-advantages-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "第一，可以表示不是函数的曲线，比如圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "advantages",
      "line_id": "advantages-3",
      "filename": "advantages-advantages-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/advantages-advantages-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "第二，自然地描述了点的运动过程，包括方向和速度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "advantages",
      "line_id": "advantages-4",
      "filename": "advantages-advantages-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/advantages-advantages-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "第三，在计算机图形学中，参数方程是绘制曲线的标准方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-1",
      "filename": "applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.28,
      "size": 20448,
      "text": "参数方程在很多领域都有应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-2",
      "filename": "applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "计算机动画中，物体的运动轨迹通常用参数方程描述。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-3",
      "filename": "applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "机器人学中，机械臂的运动路径规划使用参数曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-4",
      "filename": "applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "物理学中，抛体运动的轨迹就是参数方程的典型例子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-1",
      "filename": "summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.26,
      "size": 20160,
      "text": "让我们总结一下今天学到的内容。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-2",
      "filename": "summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "参数方程用参数 t 同时表示 x 和 y，描述点的运动轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-3",
      "filename": "summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "圆、椭圆、摆线、利萨如图形都可以用参数方程优雅地表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-4",
      "filename": "summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "参数方程在动画和图形学中有广泛应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parametric",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-5",
      "filename": "summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parametric/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "希望通过这个实验，你对参数方程有了更直观的理解！"
    }
  ],
